    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2017 Audi S5 Sportback, a vehicle that perfectly balances executive luxury with exhilarating performance. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Moonlight Blue Metallic that still catches the light beautifully; while the body is straight and free of major dings, there are minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of high-end materials. The Magma Red Nappa leather seats are soft and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver's bolster and no tears or stains. This is a non-smoker vehicle with a clean, fresh interior. Mechanically, the car is in excellent working order, featuring a responsive 3.0T V6 engine and a seamless 8-speed automatic transmission. It has been serviced regularly, with a recent oil change and a full brake inspection performed last month. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and all electronics, including the Bang & Olufsen sound system and Virtual Cockpit, function perfectly. This S5 offers a premium driving experience for someone looking for a reliable, high-performance grand tourer.",
